response.overview: After leading his football team to 15 winning seasons, coach Bill Yoast is demoted and replaced by Herman Boone – tough, opinionated and as different from the beloved Yoast as he could be. The two men learn to overcome their differences and turn a group of hostile young men into champions.
response.tagline: History is written by the winners.
response.title: Remember the Titans

titles.title: タイタンズを忘れない：2000
